      <div class="responsive-bottom-margin">
          
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>This page collates reports and tools produced by Public Health England (<abbr title="Public Health England">PHE</abbr>) to support the surveillance of coronavirus (COVID-19).</p>

</div>
</div>


  <h3 class="group-title" id="tools-and-reports">Tools and reports</h3>
    
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p><a rel="external" href="https://coronavirus.data.gov.uk/?_ga=2.126299085.1146868827.1592465517-1636247568.1558002687" class="govuk-link">COVID-19 cases in the UK dashboard</a> updated daily</p>
</div>
</div>


  <div data-module="track-click">
        <ul class="gem-c-document-list">
