  <h3 class="group-title" id="covid-19-surveillance-reports">COVID-19 surveillance reports</h3>
    
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>National surveillance reports, including weekly summary of findings monitored through various systems.</p>
</div>
</div>


