  <h3 class="group-title" id="excess-mortality-reports">Excess mortality reports</h3>
    
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Excess mortality reports, broken down by age, sex, region or upper tier local authority , ethnic group, level of deprivation, cause and place of death.</p>
</div>
</div>


