  <h3 class="group-title" id="mental-health-and-wellbeing-reports">Mental health and wellbeing reports</h3>
    
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Mental health and wellbeing surveillance reports, compiling routinely updated indicators from multiple sources and summarising important findings from ongoing surveys.</p>
</div>
</div>


